{
  "chapter": 15,
  "chapter_summary": "第15章 发财大计\n\n寇仲和徐子陵来到余杭，银两将尽，决定贩卖私盐发财。两人在盐货街买盐受阻，老刘企图敲诈被寇仲一拳击倒。海沙帮余杭分舵付舵主谭勇出现，想拉拢二人做杀手，被寇仲识破拒绝。二人决定偷盐，却遭老刘带四五十人追杀，被迫逃上一艘异国巨舶。巨舶上的神秘夫人出手相救，但因二人只求发财、无意救世济民，下令逐客。寇徐二人跳海逃生。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "现在我们已成了名人，人人都在谋我们的宝库，若我们未练成绝世神功，就往江湖闯荡，只会落得悲惨下场。但若找个地方躲起来做缩头乌龟，不但有负娘的期望，亦永远杀不了宇文化骨，你说该怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 5,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我很想再见到李大哥和素素姐姐，但高邮离扬州城那么近，而杜伏威那老蠢蛋必是到了扬州寻宝，很易遇上他呢！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "现在我们的银两所余无几，我又厌倦了去扒人的钱袋，连生活都没有着落，你教我怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "李大哥以为我们早死了，怎会在高邮等我们。你说的对，现在先要弄点钱，否则那来盘川到洛阳去找和氏壁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你有甚么发财大计？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "所有发财大计，都离不开贱入手，高放出。这里是产盐区，只要我们买他奶奶的一车盐，再偷运他鸟儿去内陆最缺盐的地方，便可将盐当黄金来换钱。那时找个安身处练起李大哥的血战十式，就不用拿着根可笑的树枝了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你知道哪处最缺盐吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你看那妞儿多么甜！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "快说！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这世上最管用就是灵活的脑筋，现在老杜截断了大江的交通。除非象宋家那种威势，谁有本事运盐到历阳以西的郡县去，所以我们若运他鸟儿的一车盐前去，就算是摆地摊都可赚个盆满钵满。来吧！要发财就来吧！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "买盐还将就着我们的财力去买，但何来余钱去买骡车呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你好象不知这人世上有手推车这种可靠的运输工具，来吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "不若我们偷上其中一条船，到大海的另一边看看，凭我们的手段，说不定能成为另一个国的皇帝，那时纳十来个贵妃，不亦乐乎。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "发财要紧，来吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "老板！我们要买货。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "老先生",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这三个月的货全给订了，你们是哪家铺子的？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "到别家去吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu",
      "speaker_name": "老刘",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "两位小兄弟面生得很，是否外来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_liu",
      "text": "我们是外地来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "老先生",
      "listener": "char_liu",
      "text": "老刘你要聊天，给我到铺外去聊，不要在这里阻碍别人交收提货。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu",
      "speaker_name": "老刘",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "看来你们又是到这里买货，以为可运往内地发财的凯子，不过却少有像你们这么年轻的，你们拿得出多少钱来？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu",
      "speaker_name": "老刘",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "走得这么容易吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你的拳头何时变得这么厉害了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "莫不是我练成了九玄大法的第一重境界，等若六份一个娘那么厉害？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_yong",
      "speaker_name": "谭勇",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "本人谭勇，乃海沙帮余杭分舵的付舵主，见两位小兄弟身手硬朗，生出想结交之心，不若找个地方，让老哥做个小东道如何？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_tan_yong",
      "text": "我们还要赶着办货去做生意呢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_yong",
      "speaker_name": "谭勇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "若两位小兄弟是要办盐货，就不要白费心了。先不说这处的货都由十多家大商号瓜分了，就算有人肯卖给你们，不但帮会要分一笔，公差要一笔，官府要一笔，到最后加上盐税，也只是白辛苦一场，赚来的都不够到窑子花三天，那还是最便宜的乡间土窑子呢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_yong",
      "speaker_name": "谭勇",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "来吧！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_yong",
      "speaker_name": "谭勇",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你两人除了拳脚功夫外，还懂甚么兵器？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_tan_yong",
      "text": "我们都是用刀的，等闲十来人都奈何不了我们。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_yong",
      "speaker_name": "谭勇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "可否让我试试小兄弟的刀法呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_tan_yong",
      "text": "真金不怕红炉火，不过谭爷最好先说出有甚么好关照，人生在世，不外求财，谭爷这么明白事理……哈！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_yong",
      "speaker_name": "谭勇",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我对两位小兄弟是一见如故，钱财只是身外物，兄弟要钱有钱，要女人有女人。待我们回去向舵主打个招呼，成了真正的拜把兄弟以后，有甚么不好商量的。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_tan_yong",
      "text": "谭爷是否看上了我们是外地来的生面人，又是两个可瞒过任何人的乳臭小子，所以想我们去为你们海沙帮刺杀另一个帮会的人，事后更可推个一干二净，嘿！这类黑锅会压死人的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "兄弟！我们走！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_yong",
      "speaker_name": "谭勇",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "且慢！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_yong",
      "speaker_name": "谭勇",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "傅小弟真厉害，那就不如摆开来说……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_tan_yong",
      "text": "你千万别说出来，若说了出来，依江湖规矩，我们就休想脱身了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_tan_yong",
      "text": "我们两兄弟到江湖上闯字号，凭的就是一身功夫，可没有打算依仗任何靠山。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "想做正常的生意人并不容易，从来能发大财的都是毫无道义的奸商，哈！我又有妙计了，今晚我们再摸到这里来，偷他鸟的一艇盐，然后溜之夭夭，连那几个子儿都省掉。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "char_kou_zhong",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "他们有那么多盐，偷十来包绝不会令他们家破人亡的吧！就偷刚才那间吧！想起那掌柜我便有气了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这真是我的好兄弟，不过做贼都该有做贼的家当，例如开锁的钢丝，防身的兵器，捆赃物的绳索诸如此类。以后吃粥还是吃饭，都要看这一铺了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "做贼的主意可是你提出来的，这些东西自然须由你去张罗。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "合则力强，分则力薄，一世人两兄弟，你也不想我一个人奔波劳碌，累得今晚连脚都动不了，只得陵弟你一个人去作贼。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "小陵！娘有教过我们空手入白刃吗？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "武士",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "滚回去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi",
      "text": "让他两人上来吧！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "武士",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "是！夫人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_bi",
      "speaker_name": "俏婢",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "两位小公子请随我来！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_qiao_bi",
      "text": "姐姐请引路！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_bi",
      "speaker_name": "俏婢",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "两位公子请进。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_bi",
      "speaker_name": "俏婢",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "两位公子请坐！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "两位小公子为何会给码头的流氓追赶呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "原来是夫人！我两兄弟先谢过援手之德。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "我们曾和他们其中一人动过手，他便召人来对付我们了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "两位小公子谈吐不俗，且身手矫健，但又似不懂武功，究竟是甚么一回事呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "我们的身手都是娘教的，读书认字，亦是由她一手包办，娘去世后，我们便四处流浪，看看有些甚么发财的生意可做……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "另一位小公子又有甚么意向呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "我们进退与共，他想发财，我自然也想发财哪！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "除了银子外，你们还想干些甚么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "夫人问得好，发财后当然要立品，最好可当个官儿，那就可光宗耀祖，八面威风了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "外面那么多人正为战乱和暴政受苦受难，你们难道没想过救世济民，为天下苍生尽点心力吗？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "我们人小力弱，三餐难继，倒不曾想过这种事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "这种大事，自有大英雄去担当的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "人各有志，两位请下船吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "这怎么行！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_bi",
      "speaker_name": "俏婢",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "两位请！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 363
    }
